# Testing (pytest)

Piramit: unit (~70%) → integration (~25%) → E2E (MVP-0 yok).

## Dosya Organizasyonu

```
tests/
  unit/           → collectors, processor, ai, auth
  integration/    → api, db, sqs
  factories/      → test data factory
  conftest.py     → db session, client fixtures
fixtures/         → JSON sample RSS, email parse
```

## Zorunlu Senaryolar

| Modül | Min test |
|-------|----------|
| Auth | login ok, wrong password, inactive user |
| RBAC | viewer → admin endpoint 403 |
| Dedup | duplicate hash skip |
| Digest | prompt parse, empty input |

## Mock Politikası

- LLM, SES, FCM, external HTTP: mock/stub
- DB integration: test PostgreSQL (CI service) veya testcontainers
- Gerçek RSS çekimi unit test'te yasak — `fixtures/` JSON

## Çalıştırma

```bash
ruff check .
mypy apps packages services
pytest tests/unit -q
pytest tests/integration -q --cov --cov-fail-under=70
```

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Test olmadan auth/RBAC değişikliği
- Production DB connection test'te
- Sleep ile async bekleme (`pytest-asyncio` + await)

